public static interface WebAppDiagnosticLogs.DefinitionStages.WithAttachForWebServerFileSystem<ParentT> extends WebAppDiagnosticLogs.DefinitionStages.WithAttach<ParentT>, WebAppDiagnosticLogs.DefinitionStages.WithQuota<ParentT>, WebAppDiagnosticLogs.DefinitionStages.WithRetentionDays<ParentT>
The final stage of the web app diagnostic log definition, plus extra settings for web server logs stored in the file system.

At this stage, any remaining optional settings can be specified, or the web app diagnostic log definition can be attached to the parent web app definition using Attachable.InDefinition.attach().
